exp = Experiment(name='test3', search_space=get_branin_search_space(),
    tracking_metrics=[BraninMetric(name='b', param_names=['x1', 'x2'])],
    runner=SyntheticRunner())

batch.add_arms_and_weights(arms=get_branin_arms(n=n, seed=0))
batch.run()
exp.new_batch_trial().add_arms_and_weights(arms=get_branin_arms(n=3 * n,
    seed=1)).run()
